  "texts": [
    "Human Annotations Annotators were contracted and managed by vendors Scale AI and Translated, which completed ethical review prior to the start of data collection.",
    "Consent for use of data for model training was obtained from all annotators through our vendors.",
    "Both Scale AI and Translated implemented several measures to prevent annotators from using LLMs as part of the annotation workflow.",
    "Scale AI engages the Anker Methodology, GISC Impact Sourcing Standard, and UN Sustainable Development Goals to provide a fair and competitive pay.",
    "The specific pay is calculated based on many factors, including the specific project, the specialized skillset and expertise required, regional costs of living and then transparently listed on Scale AI platform."
  ],
